ALL MC Versions

2.0.1

Released: 7/9/2025
  • Fixed the sidebar-topbar overlapping bug
  • Updated clients
  • Added more versions & tuff client

2.0.0

Released: 5/22/2025
  • An improved UI, that this time actually looks like the vanilla launcher
  • WASM Clients
  • Easier to manage settings
  • All the base versions from yee launcher
  • A game "console", that lets you view the logs
  • A notification system
  • Custom backgrounds
  • Games open in a new popup window, rather than on the launcher itself
  • yee launcher's cache service worker, which will allow the launcher to both work offline and boot clients faster
  • A websocket reverse proxy, which will allow you to connect to most servers over it if they are blocked at your school
  • Everything from WebMC v1* (offline downloads currently do not exist, because I am prioritizing actually releasing this and then I will add offline downloads)
